title: Have The Courage To Be Different | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Have The Courage To Be Different | Joel Osteen
description:
It's easy to get complacent when we don't see anything changing. But if you'll keep doing the right thing even when the wrong thing is happening, God will take care of getting you to the next level.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
